    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>The alarm sounds, and the house is on fire!</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras/32163de49597d13835022164874bf008.avif?t=1742188133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras_big/32163de49597d13835022164874bf008.avif?t=1742188133 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a firefighter, you must quickly extinguish the flames. But this isn't an ordinary firefighting mission: bedrooms echoing with eerie laughter, shattered mirrors everywhere, and complex mechanisms throughout the house test your wit and courage. Can you reach the source of the fire and successfully put it out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras/fd31dd1791d6b18407a9aaeb754a0610.avif?t=1742188133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras_big/fd31dd1791d6b18407a9aaeb754a0610.avif?t=1742188133 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Brave Firefighter:</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The house is on fire, and the situation is urgent! You tell your teammates to step back, and you venture alone to extinguish the source of the fire. Grab the extinguisher, put on your mask, and charge into the flames. You are the hope of the fire brigade!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Dimensional Puzzles:</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out! This house contains two worlds, and your actions will simultaneously affect both dimensions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Unlock the House's Mechanisms:</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The blocked paths, the locked doors—explore every inch of the room carefully to open the way forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras/9f687af4e857340e70a5cba8c00b4a63.avif?t=1742188133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras_big/9f687af4e857340e70a5cba8c00b4a63.avif?t=1742188133 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is created by <strong>@lightno2</strong> with YAHAHA Horror Game Kit and YAHAHA assists the creator with packaging and publishing the game based on their request. Yahaha Horror Gamekit is tailored for imaginative creators and players who adore horror games, all without the need for any programming expertise.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308940/extras/ec16e4704cac8481b1af8a559b14a25a.avif?t=1742188133\" width=720 height=216 /></span></p>",
